= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Item List =

This page documents all items in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV contains over 200 items including weapons, armor, shields, helmets, accessories, and consumable items. Items are stored starting at Bank $06.

== Item Data Structure ==

Each item uses 8 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Item Type (weapon, armor, etc.)
|-
| $01 || 1 || Stat modifier
|-
| $02 || 1 || Special effect flags
|-
| $03-$04 || 2 || Buy price (big-endian)
|-
| $05-$06 || 2 || Sell price (big-endian)
|-
| $07 || 1 || Equipment restrictions
|}

